                    </a>

                    <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/wallagram/" target="_blank" class="col-3 text-decoration-none text-black">
                        <div class="row mb-3">
                            <img src="~/img/Logos/reddit.png" class="mx-auto" style="width: 125px;" />
